I didn’t find a fantastic list of motor part numbers and how they relate to the approved motor list, so I decided to make one.

Please be aware that the data has not been double-checked. You know that old saying, trust but verify? Don’t trust and verify! If you find any errors, know of a more accurate data source, or have additional information that can be added to the sheet, please make a comment on the sheet or here. Thanks!
